OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FScotland's mental wellbeing minister
OL,7,Fhas apologised to the family of a
OL,8,Fteenager who took his own life after
OL,9,Fspending time in an adult psychiatric
OL,10,Fward.
OL,12,FTom Arthur also said he would meet
OL,13,Fwith Harris Macdonell's family and
OL,14,Fadmitted the lack of age-appropriate
OL,15,Fbeds for young people suffering from
OL,16,Fsevere mental health issues was
OL,17,F'unacceptable.'
