OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FHe was responding to calls from
OL,7,FHarris' mother Jane, for "real action"
OL,8,Fto address the lack of beds for
OL,9,Fchildren and young people.
OL,11,FShe said: "My message to them is that
OL,12,Fwe don't want to hear any more
OL,13,Fplatitudes about this. We want some
OL,14,Freal action and we want a strategy for
OL,15,Fhow they are going to address this. I
OL,16,Frealise it is a complicated issue, but
OL,17,Fthere have to be better options than
OL,18,Fwhat Harris experienced and that's the
OL,19,Fbottom line."
