OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FMr Arthur said: "It shouldn't have
OL,7,Fhappened and I am deeply sorry that it
OL,8,Fdid happen. There is significant
OL,9,Finvestment underway to expand the
OL,10,Frange of services that CAMHS can
OL,11,Fprovide and that includes acute
OL,12,Finpatient psychiatric support as well."
