OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FHe added: "What happened to Harris was
OL,7,Fcompletely unacceptable. I think the
OL,8,Fpeople in Scotland can have confidence
OL,9,Fin our health and social care service,
OL,10,Fbut when the service provided is not
OL,11,Fwhat's required and when there are
OL,12,Ffailings, lessons must be learned and
OL,13,FI am committed to making sure that we
OL,14,Fdo learn those lessons."
OL,16,FHarris Macdonell died on August 19th
OL,17,F2020, at the age of 19, near his home
OL,18,Fin Lilliesleaf in the Scottish Borders.
