OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FIn 2018, aged 16, Harris spent nine
OL,7,Fnights in Huntlyburn, NHS Borders'
OL,8,Fadult psychiatric ward near Melrose,
OL,9,Fbefore a bed became available in a
OL,10,Fyoung persons unit in Edinburgh.
OL,12,FLast week a Fatal Accident Inquiry
OL,13,Fsaid that it was "wholly
OL,14,Finappropriate" for young people to be
OL,15,Ftreated in adult wards.
OL,17,FIt concluded Harris' death couldn't
OL,18,Fhave been prevented.
OL,26,@uD@ROUvD@NO]
