OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FJane, who worked as a paediatric
OL,7,Fconsultant for 30 years, is convinced
OL,8,Fher son's experience in an adult unit
OL,9,Fwas responsible for him failing to
OL,10,Ftalk with health professionals in the
OL,11,Ffinal months of his life.
OL,13,FShe said: "He was never the same boy
OL,14,Fagain. He found it difficult to attend
OL,15,Fappointments, he gave very little
OL,16,Faway, he was guarded. I think his
OL,17,Freluctance to engage was really fear
OL,18,Fto engage with them from that point
OL,19,Fonwards."
OL,26,@uD@KOU{D@IO]
