OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,F"The absolute bottom line is that you
OL,7,Fhave a young person in an adult ward,
OL,8,Fwho's becoming distressed, that needs
OL,9,Fto be an emergency. That's not
OL,10,Facceptable."
OL,12,FFigures obtained by the Scottish
OL,13,FConservatives show that, since Harris
OL,14,Fwas in Huntlyburn ward in 2018, there
OL,15,Fhave been 57 admissions of children
OL,16,Fand young people.
OL,18,FOfficial figures show that across
OL,19,FScotland, in the year up to March
OL,20,F2024, 59 under-18s were treated in
OL,21,Fadult facilities.
