OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We expect children and young
OL,8,Fpeople who need inpatient mental
OL,9,Fhealth care to be looked after in age-
OL,10,Fappropriate specialist facilities.
OL,12,F"On occasions where young people are
OL,13,Fplaced within an adult ward this will
OL,14,Fbe monitored and reviewed regularly to
OL,15,Fensure that the young person is
OL,16,Freceiving the most appropriate
OL,17,Ftreatment and care."
