OL,3,CMinister apologises to family of
OL,4,Cteenager who took his own life
OL,6,FNHS Borders said: "The purpose of the
OL,7,FInquiry was to establish the
OL,8,Fcircumstances of Harris' death and to
OL,9,Fconsider what steps, if any, may be
OL,10,Ftaken to prevent other deaths in
OL,11,Fsimilar circumstances. Our staff have
OL,12,Fengaged fully and openly with the
OL,13,FInquiry. We respect the Sheriff's
OL,14,Fdetermination that, in considering the
OL,15,Fevidence submitted, Harris' death
OL,16,Fcould not have been predicted or
OL,17,Fprevented."
